data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the vibrant Cutter Park neighborhood! Step inside and admire the beautiful open concept floor plan with wide plank engineered wood floors throughout. The main level features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, while downstairs offers 2 more bedrooms and 1 full bath. 
Enjoy the amazing views of the pond visible from the bright, modern kitchen, living room, and deck. This property offers beautiful curb appeal, idyllic views, all within a lovely neighborhood. This location can not be beat! Call today for your private showing!
